nodes.text: Rorhy Etamuhs was a male Human soldier of the Galactic Republic during the revolt against the Eternal Empire. In 3630 BBY he was part of the forces brought by the Republic Supreme Commander Jace Malcom to Iokath.
Rorhy Etamuhs appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Eternal Throne as a vendor on Iokath for Republic-affiliated players.
